  "content": {
    "sfdetails__c": "<p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"auto\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ItjbI2hYg7o?si=JDCQt6agYZoT68F3\" title=\"YouTube video player\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>In this video, AskF5 shows you how you can use the Configuration utility to review BIG-IP log files, which contain important diagnostic information about events occurring on the BIG-IP system.</p>\n<p>This demonstration uses BIG-IP 15.0.1.</p>"
